appletv
Apple TV Software beta 3

This is a pre-release version of Apple TV Software to be used for testing AirPlay with your iOS apps.


Downloads

    Apple TV Software beta (3rd generation Rev A)
    Apple TV Software beta (3rd generation)
    Apple TV Software beta (2nd generation)




Please only take what you need to save on my bandwidth. I only have an upload speed of 1.5-2 MB/s, so please be patient.

Please also seed to at least a 1:1 ratio.

All items are in conveniently named .dmg files.
The .ipsw files are the only files in these containers.

Macs have no problem with DMG files. PC users please use google to figure it out. I believe UltraISO opens these files.

I take no responsibility for what may happen to your device with this build. Remember that it is still on at beta stage, so you may encounter issues.

Use responsibly.
